│ From this log, I identified the first transformation point as:                │
│                                                                               │
│ ```                                                                           │
│ llvm/include/llvm/IR/DataLayout.h::llvm::DataLayout::getTypeSizeInBits()      │
│ ```                                                                           │
│                                                                               │
